@startuml
actor User
participant MobileApp
participant Database
participant PaymentGateway

User -> MobileApp: Login request
MobileApp -> Database: Validate credentials
Database --> MobileApp: Credentials valid
MobileApp --> User: Login success

User -> MobileApp: Browse guitars
MobileApp -> Database: Fetch guitar list
Database --> MobileApp: Guitar data
MobileApp --> User: Display guitars

User -> MobileApp: Add to cart
MobileApp -> Database: Update cart
Database --> MobileApp: Cart updated
MobileApp --> User: Cart updated

User -> MobileApp: Purchase
MobileApp -> PaymentGateway: Process payment
PaymentGateway --> MobileApp: Payment success
MobileApp -> Database: Create order
Database --> MobileApp: Order created
MobileApp --> User: Purchase complete
@enduml
